CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS "markman";

CREATE TYPE "markman"."bookmarkType" AS ENUM('folder', 'bookmark');

CREATE TABLE "markman"."bookmarks" (
	"id" integer PRIMARY KEY GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY (sequence name "markman"."bookmarks_id_seq" INCREMENT BY 1 MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 2147483647 START WITH 1 CACHE 1),
	"chromeId" integer NOT NULL,
	"type" "markman"."bookmarkType" NOT NULL,
	"isPinned" boolean DEFAULT false,
	"pinOrder" integer,
	"title" varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	"url" varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	"domain" varchar(255),
	"favicon" varchar(255),
	"createdAt" timestamp NOT NULL,
	"updatedAt" timestamp,
	"parentId" integer NOT NULL,
	"tags" integer[] DEFAULT ARRAY[]::integer[] NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE "markman"."tags" (
	"id" integer PRIMARY KEY GENERATED BY DEFAULT AS IDENTITY (sequence name "markman"."tags_id_seq" INCREMENT BY 1 MINVALUE 1 MAXVALUE 2147483647 START WITH 1 CACHE 1),
	"name" varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	"color" varchar(255) NOT NULL,
	"createdAt" timestamp NOT NULL,
	"updatedAt" timestamp
);
